item.title: TIM CANOVA RAISES $557,000 IN FIRST QUARTER IN RACE AGAINST DEBBIE WASSERMAN SCHULTZ
item.description:
TIM CANOVA RAISES $557,000 IN FIRST QUARTER IN RACE AGAINST DEBBIE WASSERMAN SCHULTZ

Tim Canova said Monday he's raised more than $557,000 in the first quarter of 2016 in his bid to unseat Democratic National Committee Chairwoman Debbie Wasserman Schultz from her South Florida congressional seat. That's more money than any previous first-time candidate has accumulated in the first quarter of the election year.

item.description:
The Panama Papers Scandal Will Put Bernie Sanders In The White House. Here's Why
